summary: A vibrant ENB preset with realistic yet atmospheric interiors, visible nights and vibrant days with a crisp image, and good performance. Also works very well with RLO and CoT.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7442/9373279240_8bac9d6c55_b.jpg[/img]

[color=green][b]PLEASE ENJOY! And add screenshots of your own as well! It would make me a very happy lady! :)[/b][/color]
[line]

[heading][color=red][b]NEW MAIN FILE 2.0 WITH IMPROVED INTERIORS AND BUILT-IN DEPTH OF FIELD HAS BEEN UPLOADED![/b][/color][/heading]

[line]

[color=green]This is not exactly performance friendly for less powerful rigs due to highly enhanced graphics and lighting, I have a 2 GB HD Radeon 6950, AMD Quad Core CPU and 8 GB RAM and I get between 30 - 50 FPS outdoors and 50-60 FPS indoors with no stuttering or problems. I use this with the v.014 DLL and it works well with the new updates as well. It also works with older DLL's as well in my experience. It comes with SweetFX to further enhance visuals.[/color]

[line]

[color=green][heading]COMPATIBILITY[/color][/heading]

[color=green]Climates of Tamriel? Yes, it works very well with CoT.

Realistic Lighting Overhaul? YES, Completely. I HIGHLY RECOMMEND RLO. :D

Enhanced Lights and FX? In my experience yes it does work, but I personally very much prefer RLO, but whatever floats your boat. :)[/color]
